<div class="visual-detail">

  <a href="../3-visuals.html" class="back-link">← Back to Visuals</a>

  <h2 class="visual-title">Spanish River Basin Districts</h2>

  <div class="visual-detail-media">
    <img src="../images/visuals/plot2.png" alt="Spanish river basins"/>
  </div>

  <div class="visual-meta">
    <p class="visual-desc">Map of Spain's 16 river basin districts overlaid with the HydroRIVERS dataset. Each basin is coloured independently, with river networks drawn at varying widths according to stream order. Reservoir and gauge station locations are marked as dots.</p>
    <table class="visual-info">
      <tr><td class="meta-label">Tools</td><td>Python · GeoPandas · Matplotlib</td></tr>
      <tr><td class="meta-label">Context</td><td>#30DayMapChallenge 2025 · Day: Rivers</td></tr>
      <tr><td class="meta-label">Data</td><td>Spanish River Basin Districts (MITECO, 2023) · HydroRIVERS (Lehner & Grill, 2013)</td></tr>
    </table>
  </div>

</div>

<style>
.visual-detail {
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 1rem 1rem 3rem 1rem;
}
.back-link {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  color: #e8a020 !important;
  font-weight: 600;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
}
.back-link:hover {
  text-decoration: underline;
}
.visual-title {
  font-size: 1.6rem;
  color: #e8a020 !important;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.visual-detail-media img,
.visual-detail-media video {
  width: 100%;
  border-radius: 10px;
  box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
  display: block;
}
.visual-meta {
  margin-top: 1.8rem;
}
.visual-desc {
  font-size: 1rem;
  line-height: 1.7;
  color: #333;
  margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  text-align: justify;
}
.visual-info {
  border: none;
  width: 100%;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
}
.visual-info td {
  padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem 0.4rem 0;
  border: none;
  vertical-align: top;
}
.meta-label {
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #94805c;
  white-space: nowrap;
  width: 80px;
}
</style>
```

